                  </hi>. I am a linen-draper, and live at Clapham. I had a piece of printed cotton safe at my door at half-past twelve o'clock on the 23rd of Oct.—I received information from a neighbour, and missed it be<lb></lb>tween twelve and one—this is it—it is mine.</p>
